{
  "stem": "13469.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were shaven off by then kind of thing, but nevertheless, the lice got in your hair, and under your arms, and in the seams of your clothes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we turned all our clothes inside out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And in the seams of the clothes were the lice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we'd pick them out and squash them to death kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was-- all day we spent doing that kind of thing, all of us-- great fun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we realized that it was the lice that was spreading the typhus epidemic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And just-- they were just everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You'd kill them all one day, and they would be there next day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The beds were infested with the lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And everybody had the lice everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we knew nothing about the gassing and all these other things, that I was aware of.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, some people must have heard the stories, because for example, this Dutch woman who claims to have spoken to Anne Frank and her sister across the wire, I think Anne Frank just said, when they asked about certain people, they just said they weren't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether they said why or how, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, these are only reconstructions, anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We can't remember having heard anything there about gas chambers and about everybody being killed, that sort of thing, no.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- wee couldn't meet with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still isolated in our particular section.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's actually an interesting story by this Regina Franks, who died, committed suicide last week.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was an Auschwitz survivor, came to Belsen in January '45.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I told my story one day, she was in the audience.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And afterwards, she said she saw those people in that separate section of the camp with the yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
